{"tid":1997931,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"港島西 租樓","createTime":"2020-05-02T04:45:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T12:41:52.000Z","uid":248790,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5b4349bee24c5b525054849876b412ceab4959db","tid":1997931,"uid":248790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T04:45:47.000Z","msg":"筆直 大約12-3k<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同女朋友諗住搬出黎自己住<br />\n想住港島西貪佢返工近/跑步放狗又方便<br />\n<br />\nTarget啲舊屋苑/單支甚至唐樓都得<br />\n暫時望緊<strong>嘉輝花園 </strong>同 <strong>創業中心</strong><br />\n巴打們覺得邊度好啲？<br />\n或者有無其他介紹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地都無乜大要求<br />\n最緊要樓下條街唔太污糟/廁所企理<br />\n同埋附近有得月租車位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e2a9a5d527c772e8e6bc043b7b060d396ccb6c9","tid":1997931,"uid":58503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b4349bee24c5b525054849876b412ceab4959db","tid":1997931,"uid":248790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T04:45:47.000Z","msg":"筆直 大約12-3k<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同女朋友諗住搬出黎自己住<br />\n想住港島西貪佢返工近/跑步放狗又方便<br />\n<br />\nTarget啲舊屋苑/單支甚至唐樓都得<br />\n暫時望緊<strong>嘉輝花園 </strong>同 <strong>創業中心</strong><br />\n巴打們覺得邊度好啲？<br />\n或者有無其他介紹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地都無乜大要求<br />\n最緊要樓下條街唔太污糟/廁所企理<br />\n同埋附近有得月租車位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T04:59:56.000Z","msg":"論方便，創業中心一定好d，而且樓下有月租車位。不過我反而好奇你嘅筆直夠唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23108110cc173ddb9c33a6b9e7bf60a2e4